locality: Madagascar. Prov. Toliara. S of Toliara near Saint Augustin. Calcareous rocks. Much branched shrub, c. 2 m. Flowers blue, sympetalous.

District Amboasary Sud, Commune et Fokontany Anadabolava, Aire Protégée Vohidava-Betsimalaho, le long de la rivière Vandamena, affluent du fleuve de Mandrare, Andafiana Iamitory. Herbier conservé en alcool. Guide : Bonnet et Fiarova.
SE of Tulear on Route Nationale 7, 15 km from town near La Table.
